data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home nestled on over 1 acre. This property features a long driveway that provides privacy and gorgeous trees for plenty of shade.  This is a great location, close to I-10, for an easy interstate commute. This home has a convenient layout with a large living area with a fireplace that creates an inviting atmosphere. The master bedroom features two en-suite bathrooms which provides convenience and privacy. Additionally, the home offers two water heaters to ensure a steady supply of hot water.  The spacious kitchen is sure to impress with modern appliances and plenty of counter and cabinet space. The walk-in pantry provides ample space for storing groceries and supplies. The oversized utility room allows for plenty of space for all your laundry needs. The covered carport includes a large attached storage room and workshop area, perfect for storing tools, equipment, yard toys, or whatever you heart desires. An additional shed in the backyard provides more storage to help keep the house and yard organized and clutter free. Make this remarkable and functional property yours! All information and measurements to be verified by buyer and buyer’s agent.
